A scholarly art? <br>
<br>
It can be, but for the most part it involves blowing things up with loud report. You can philosophize all you want about the nature of Wizardry powers; whether you should fight good or evil; whether unjust means are ok if they lead to just ends. All of these things are meaningless. You <!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong>ARE</strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END--> a Wizard, it should be in your <!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong>BLOOD</strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END-->, if it is not, may I suggest a change of <!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong><!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><em>professions</em><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--></strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END-->.<br>
